<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4418086>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 6. Geographic distributions of Okanagana boweni sp. n. and Okanagana simulata, and the California range of their hypothesized host plant Artemisia tridentata (data provided by the participants of the Consortium of California Herbaria ucjeps. berkeley.edu/consortium/). The yellow hatched polygon outlines the Walker Lane region (Carlson et al. 2013). The inset details the type locality." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4418086/files/figure.png" .

